title: Wiki
text:
Wiki
The aim of this is to:
Be very easy to use from an organisation/logistics point of view: no need to build anything or run anything To be totally doable and quick through the browser To encourage inclusion of useful team-relevant information (requiring a pull request) To be regularly pruned etc., but also to have a secure version control history so previous versions can be found if needed To work identically to just a plain git repo but with better in-file searching.
